  "title": "Enterprise Architect (Cloud, Infrastructure)",
  "description": "<p><strong>Enterprise Architect(Infrastructure)/ Solution Architect (Software)</strong></p><p><br /></p><p><br /></p><p>Our Esteemed and Reputable Client is looking for 2 headcount as an</p><p><strong>Enterprise Architect(Infrastructure)/ Solution Architect (Software).</strong></p><p></p><p><strong>Requirements:</strong></p><ul><li><strong>Strong involvement as Enterprise Architect/ Solution Architect.</strong></li><li><strong>Good in Cloud Infrastructure (GCC, Saas etc)</strong></li><li><strong>Technically incline in Network Infrastructure and Cyber Security.</strong></li><li><strong>Good in Network and Security Design.</strong></li><li><strong>Knowledge of Software Application Solution is Preferred.</strong></li><li><strong>Experience in Software Sales or Pre-Sales Consulting</strong></li><li>Main support for cyber-security solution design, presale and post-sale deployment of security solution.</li><li>Good in Stakeholders/ Clients Management.</li><li><strong>Involved in Pre and Post sales/ Consultation for Clients and Stakeholders.</strong></li><li>Experience in high level design, implementation and technical requirements management. </li><li>Provide consultation to Stakeholders and Clients on Architecting matter.</li><li>Minimum 6 years of Solution Architect/ Enterprise Architect experience.</li><li>Possess Government / System Integrator domain (Preferred).</li><li>Possess Government domain background.</li><li>Singaporean Only</li></ul><p></p><p></p><p>If you feel that you have the skill-sets that we are looking for, please apply in-confidence with an updated MS Word Resume to: jeline@starcareerconsulting.com</p><p></p><p>We regret only shortlisted candidate would be contacted.</p><p><br /></p><p></p><p><strong>Yong Jeline (Reg. No. R1101621)</strong></p><p><strong>STAR CAREER CONSULTING PTE LTD (EA License: 20C0353)</strong></p>",
